title: Ant-Man 003 (2015) (Digital) (Zone-Empire)
description: Ant-Man faces off against his deadliest arch-enemy -- the mercenary known as TASKMASTER! Can we really call him an 'arch-enemy'? Well, they've actually fought a bunch of times (look it up). And they definitely don't like each other -- that's what 'arch' means, right? There's a mystery villain pulling the strings! He's the one covered in heavy shadow. Mystery villains never have good lighting. Need to get to an Ikea or something
